do con los comentarios de Lucero (el Demonio) y sus acompañantes (Envidia, Inteligencia, Ciencia, Conjetura), en una disposición de numerosos y breves momentos dramáticos y narrativos, en los que historia sagrada, símbolo, visualidad teatral y dimensión didáctica se funden en una pieza que exhibe la característica multiplicidad de intereses intelectuales y poéticos de la monja novohispana.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn Spanish, Castilian.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 27. Jan 2023) 0aMexican literaturey17th century. 0aSpanish American literaturey17th century. 7aPERFORMING ARTS / Theater / General.2bisacsh1 aArellano, Ignacio, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aRice, Robin Ann, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2020 Part 2z978311069629508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Arts 2020z9783110704655oZDB-23-DPK08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020z9783110704518oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertVervuert Complete eBook-Package 2020z9783110689631oZDB-207-IBV0 cprintz978849192144840uhttps://doi.org/10.31819/978396456980640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783964569806423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783964569806/original  a978-3-11-069629-5  DG Plus PP Package 2020 Part 2b2020  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_MUAR  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-207-IBVb2020  aZDB-23-DGGb2020  aZDB-23-DPKb2020